<template>
    <el-table :data="tableData" :height="tableHeight" style="width: 100%">
      <el-table-column
        prop="date"
        label="日期"
        width="301.33">
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
        prop="name"
        label="姓名"
        width="301.33">
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
        prop="address"
        label="地址">
      </el-table-column>
    </el-table>
  </template>
<script>
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        labelPosition: 'right',
        formLabelAlign: {
          name: '',
          region: '',
          type: ''
        }
      };
    }
  }
</script>
